---

<ApplicationLayout
  title="Alfa Laval G2-40 Decanter | High Performance Centrifuge"
  pageTitle="Alfa Laval G2-40 Decanter | High-Performance Centrifuge"
  disableTitleSuffix={true}
  description="Alfa Laval G2-40 decanter centrifuge finds multiple uses for sludge thickening and wastewater applications. It is ideal for high sludge mining applications."
  heroImage="/images/alfa-laval-g2-40-decanter/alfa-laval-g2-40-decanter-2000.webp"
  heroImageAlt="Alfa Laval G2-40 Decanter Centrifuge"
  category="products"
  categoryLabel="Products"
  canonicalUrl="https://dolphincentrifuge.com/alfa-laval-g2-40-decanter/"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  toc={toc}
  relatedApplications={relatedApplications}
  relatedProducts={relatedProducts}
>

  <!-- Alfa Laval G2-40 Two-Phase Decanter Centrifuge -->
  <h2 id="g2-40-decanter">Alfa Laval G2-40 Two-Phase Decanter Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The <a href="https://www.alfalaval.us/products/separation/centrifugal-separators/decanters/sg2/">Alfa Laval G2-40</a> <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/">Decanter Centrifuge</a> is a horizontal de-sludging centrifuge built for the two-phase separation of <strong>wastewater</strong>, <strong>crude oil tank bottoms</strong>, municipal <strong>sludge-thickening</strong>, industrial sludge dewatering, <strong>paint sludge handling</strong>, etc.</p>

  <p>With a 25 HP Motor, the G2-40 decanter has a <strong>bowl RPM of 4,000</strong> and can process <strong>160 GPM of water with light sludge</strong>.</p>

  <!-- Applications -->
  <h3 id="applications">Applications</h3>

  <p>The Alfa Laval G2-40 Decanter is used for the following applications.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><a href="/hemp-extraction-centrifuge/">Hemp Solvent Extraction</a></li>
    <li><a href="/ethanol-extraction-centrifuges-technical-comparison/">Ethanol Extraction Centrifuge</a></li>
    <li><a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/">Waste Oil De-sludging</a></li>
    <li><a href="/crude-oil-centrifuge/">Crude Oil Tank Bottom Sludge</a></li>
    <li><a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">Municipal Wastewater</a></li>
    <li><a href="/centrifuge-pyrolysis-oil/">Pyrolysis Sludge Separation</a></li>
    <li><a href="/liquid-humus-centrifuge/">Liquid Humus Fertilizer</a></li>
    <li><a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">Sludge Thickening &amp; Dewatering</a></li>
  </ul>

  <figure class="img-cap-800">
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-g2-40-decanter/Alfa-Laval-Decanter-Rotating-Assembly-800.webp"
      alt="Alfa Laval G2 Decanter Rotating Assembly"
      width="800"
      height="352"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <figcaption><strong>Alfa Laval G2 Decanter</strong></figcaption>
  </figure>

  <!-- Cross Section Diagram -->
  <h3 id="cross-section-diagram">Cross Section Diagram</h3>

  <figure class="img-cap-600">
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-g2-40-decanter/Decanter-Cross-Section-600.webp"
      alt="Decanter Cross Section"
      width="600"
      height="264"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <figcaption><strong>Decanter Centrifuge Cross Section</strong></figcaption>
  </figure>

  <!-- Specifications -->
  <h3 id="specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
    <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
      <tbody>
        <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Model Type</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Alfa Laval G2-40 Decanter Centrifuge</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Rated Capacity</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">160 GPM on Water Sludge Thickening</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Auger Differential Speed</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">1 ~ 140 RPM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Drive Motor Power</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">20 HP</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">GearBox Ratio</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">1: 52 (3.5 kN-M) DD Gearbox</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">A<sub>E</sub> (Area Equivalent)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">1,565</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Bowl Speed</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">4,000 RPM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">G-Force</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">3,150 RCF</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Conveyor Protection</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Carbide Tile or Tungsten Carbide Hard-Surfacing</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- PDF Datasheet - after specs table -->
  <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-4">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 shrink-0 text-red-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
      <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-6-6zm-1 1.5L18.5 9H13V3.5zM8.5 15.5h-.75v1.25H7v-4h1.5c.83 0 1.5.67 1.5 1.5s-.67 1.25-1.5 1.25zm3.75 1.25h-1.5v-4H12c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2s-.9 2-2 2zm4.5-2.75h-1v.75h1v.75h-1v1.25h-.75v-4H17v.75h-1v.5h1v-.25z"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="flex-1">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Alfa Laval G2 Decanter - Product Datasheet</p>
      <a
        href="/images/alfa-laval-g2-40-decanter/Alfa-Laval-G2-Decanter.pdf"
        class="text-sm text-gold hover:underline font-medium"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        download
      >Download PDF</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</ApplicationLayout>
